{"tid":483320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誤拒港童入境　澳門保安司：無問題","createTime":"2017-11-29T04:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T10:39:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"837fdb1d3079be43e11814abcc578711e59133a6","tid":483320,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171129/20228937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171129%2F20228937&d=wpymXzIE9pr1X%2Be76RV4UG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f06ad98d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171129%2F20228937&h=47b62bac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171129/20228937</a><br />\n<br />\n誤拒港童入境　澳門保安司：無問題<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171129/large/16137262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171129%2Flarge%2F16137262.jpg&h=7b1338c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門保安司黃少澤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近年澳門當局以對「內部保安的穩定構成威脅」為由，拒絕本港社運、泛民人士和傳媒入境，甚至有一歲港童被拒入境，社會譁然。澳門保安司黃少澤指有責任維護本地安全，認為此舉無問題，並指澳門反恐屬「三無」，即無風險、無情報、無線索，反恐級別屬低級程度。<br />\n<br />\n稱當地反恐「三無」<br />\n<br />\n澳門立法會昨就保安領域進行施政辯論，泛民議員區錦新指，澳門當局近年不斷以《內部保安綱要法》無理拒絕港人入境，甚至有一歲港童「遭殃」。保安司黃少澤指，任何國家和地區都有權維護本地安全，不認為有問題，更列舉美國將國家列為禁止入境對象，澳門只是按每宗個案處理，在充份情報及分析下針對某些人，「人哋針對一個國家就冇問題，點解我唔可以咁做？」他希望社會理解，維護本地安全是每名市民的責任。但他承認一歲小童被禁入境個案是警方犯錯，若再發生會提出紀律程序。<br />\n<br />\n間選議員葉兆佳指現時香港反恐級別屬中級，問及澳門反恐屬哪個級別，黃少澤指澳門反恐屬「三無」，即無風險、無情報、無線索，反恐級別屬低級。席間區錦新聞言笑起來，黃竟叫區「唔好笑」，指相關判斷是根據香港方面的指數，經過充份分析和研究，「唔係我隨口噏，區議員你都有義務，每個市民都有責任同埋義務，你可以批評警方執法工作，但你唔可以笑，你笑係對警隊唔尊重同唔支持」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，區錦新質疑警方濫用加重違令罪，檢控參與社會行動人士，黃少澤強調警方依法執法，不執法才是失職，指2014年至今有1,882次集會及147次遊行，其中12次遊行和兩次集會，共58人涉加重違令，他反問為何其他遊行集會人士守法，而該14次卻發生涉嫌違法事件。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明"},{"pid":"d83e5abc400efc668a74f4d4f23913b6429aae67","tid":483320,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾官僚！"},{"pid":"ca191cf875884e2e4ad393a42a13db11c6c7910f","tid":483320,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5a4da4258eb96e6f9a3d9a212673002a480793","tid":483320,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"美國有兩架飛機剷入世貿，澳門發生過咩事咁巴閉要同人地相提並論"},{"pid":"494c6bef2106b073941c4c36874fa2e86d0313b8","tid":483320,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"香港應禁止澳門政府係香港買廣告宣傳旅遊"},{"pid":"684538d3dc4659c572f125a766d0d56f0680f8f8","tid":483320,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"所以話唔怪得香港人憎澳門人"},{"pid":"14aebf49ecefd2f3a2efbbf9a5d063fd0de63ee4","tid":483320,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港應禁止澳門政府係香港買廣告宣傳旅遊</blockquote><br />\n有本事直接禁晒香港人入境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7457922d0973460ac52ad4ecfc5b6447cc7e64fd","tid":483320,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"上次隻鴿係天譴，再係咁奶共下次再黎多幾隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4ddbe59cac0f2470b20d37c6b8f5bd313708fb","tid":483320,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"死澳門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6302ce1bbcd258f21e7a8d458c297fe7d4cb33","tid":483320,"uid":37413,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"點解澳門狗成日覺得啲人會入嚟澳門犯法<br />\n心諗你澳門有乜撚嘢咁巴閉吸引人嚟犯案，我印象好似冇乜人入澳門犯案喎，打比喻即係一個暗瘡肥婆著夾萬底褲鎖住個閪又唔比男人接近，屌你照吓鏡先啦好唔好！"},{"pid":"aba3b335389bd1182a2880719f8110505c46874a","tid":483320,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:57:44.000Z","msg":"禁止澳門人入境 要入院就幫襯謀財同害命啦"},{"pid":"40cb8a5f7db6da369b85cdc99d013562091ea8cd","tid":483320,"uid":142888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"香港入境處都禁止咗英國政治人物入境啦，嗰法律基礎和理由仲比澳門少同荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最搞笑係社會完全唔重視呢件事，冇人屌政府同入境處，林鄭話唔排除未來彭定康會被拒入境，都一樣冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a9f3a61f23686cf0f1732998305b86288c6bdc","tid":483320,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次隻鴿係天譴，再係咁奶共下次再黎多幾隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐巴士,cat 5登陸,造成破壞分分鐘同Katrina有得揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66742772d5c4f83c2043cac150f29322a1649b36","tid":483320,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾官"}]}